trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameElement class represents a configuration element for a service name used in a <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: ServiceNameElement 클래스는 서비스 이름에 사용 되는 구성 요소를 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> class.

When this constructor is used to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> class, the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: 이 생성자의 새 인스턴스를 초기화 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>클래스는 <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>속성이 `null`.</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property should be set to an appropriate value for the application before calling the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> method to add the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> instance to the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>속성은 <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>클래스</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> 인스턴스</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> 를 추가 하는 메서드</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> 를 호출 하기 전에 응용 프로그램에 대 한 적절 한 값 설정</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Service Provider Name (SPN) for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: 이 대 한 서비스 공급자 이름 (SPN)를 가져오거나 <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> 인스턴스.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the representation of SPN for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>이 SPN의 표현이 포함 된 <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref> 인스턴스.</xref:System.String>
